subject: Aborigines
Olympic Games
Ice Dancing
Figure Skating
lead_paragraph: Russian ice dancers Oksana Domnina and Maxim Shabalin have joined a long tradition of questionable costume choices, but theirs has drawn the ire of aboriginal leaders.
